<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<title>Verify Your Account - iGreenMon</title>
	</head>

	<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 2rem; color: #333">
		<h2>Welcome to iGreenMon!</h2>
		<p>Hi <%= name %></p>
		<p>
			Thank you for signing up. To complete your registration, please
			verify your account by clicking the button below:
		</p>
		<p style="margin: 2rem 0">
			<a
				href="<%= link %>"
				style="
					background-color: #4caf50;
					color: white;
					padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
					text-decoration: none;
					border-radius: 5px;
				"
				>Verify Account</a
			>
		</p>
		<p>
			If you did not sign up for iGreenMon, you may safely ignore this
			email.
		</p>
		<p style="margin-top: 2rem">Warm regards,<br />The iGreenMon Team</p>
	</body>
</html>
